{"tid":2152010,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教局教材談人權稱勿以公義之名違法 律師批教材重限制輕權利","createTime":"2020-08-11T16:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T17:22:45.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7782f781f07fbbc3bd62ecbf6354482435ce3264","tid":2152010,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T16:54:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/AMQAQSDAZ6BEPJPU7B67F453AM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FAMQAQSDAZ6BEPJPU7B67F453AM%2F&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=0abc9097\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FAMQAQSDAZ6BEPJPU7B67F453AM%2F&h=12678e2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/AMQAQSDAZ6BEPJPU7B67F453AM/</a><br />\n<br />\n該份名為「人權與法治」的簡報，首3頁是有關法治的基本含義、法律面前人人平等之類的簡介；之後3頁則引述《香港人權法案條例》中有關發表、集會和結社的權利，以及相關的規限；其後12頁均有關權利的限制，例如引述政府新聞公報指「為維持公共衞生而限制市民聚集」、引述終審法院首席法官馬道立演辭指「享用或堅持個人權利&hellip;&hellip;不能成為損害他人人身安全或財產，或使用暴力的藉口」，以及引述律師會會長彭韻僖言論指「『即使違法仍可維護法治』乃一明顯謬誤」等。<br />\n<br />\n人權律師莊耀洸檢視簡報後指出，簡報只有3頁介紹法治、3頁較均衡地提及權利和限制，其餘12頁全部都着重對權利的限制，在篇幅上重限制而輕權利，未能反映對公權力的限制，反而強調對個人的限制，作為人權教育明顯不足。<br />\n<br />\n在取材上，通識科教師田方澤質疑簡報只選用律師會會長彭韻僖的演辭，卻沒有選擇取態較開明的大律師公會前主席石永泰演辭，從教學專業角度便是不夠全面，未能呈現不同的觀點，而只是灌輸政府的觀點。"},{"pid":"1e6cfdbc7866a43372855badb5bf78734b75e697","tid":2152010,"uid":132462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T17:13:58.000Z","msg":"話你聽就算踩你踩到上心口 你都要跟佢個規矩玩<br />\n<br />\n唔跟呀？國安法拉鳩你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5cf605ec4eb49c59d3fe2a5d52e1745c2fb643","tid":2152010,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T17:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/YwIk7z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FYwIk7z.jpg&h=b3b740ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5t5YP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5t5YP.jpg&h=bf84654d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/36/83359569_29c282822a_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F36%2F83359569_29c282822a_c.jpg&h=94bf8981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/b4/ab/48/b4ab480f71b11be5bd9485ca641e0f79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Fb4%2Fab%2F48%2Fb4ab480f71b11be5bd9485ca641e0f79.jpg&h=8f82ee00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n8WA7EO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn8WA7EO.jpg&h=fe302ad7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c502143ee187080dc0daa70db0bf8bab42034df","tid":2152010,"uid":173002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T17:22:45.000Z","msg":"共產黨暴力手段推翻中華民國合法嘅國民政府，共產黨都係違法，而且血腥暴力、恐怖主義。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}